<L>In its full length, and &s;pin it to the la&s;t,</L>
<L>So &s;hall we gain Bill o<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> day <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">.</L></Q>
<Q><L>A day, an have of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"></L>
