<P>YOUR Oration delivered on the 16th in&s;t. was not only highly acceptable to the audience, but we think calculated to render community a &s;ervice, if made public. In behalf of the company, therefore, we re|turn you our thanks for your ingenious per|formance, and reque&s;t a copy for the pre&s;s.</P>
<CLOSER><SIGNED><HI>With re&s;pect, we are &s;ir, Your friends,</HI>
